A test yii framework webservice to measure the tweet density of a user. 

The webservice takes the following parameter
type: string can be {"html", "xml", "json"}
handle: string (eg: 'interviewstreet', 'twitter')
count: integer X (number of tweets to analyze)

Chk Out: http://tweetstats.com/graphs/interviewstreet and http://xefer.com/twitter/interviewstreet
